    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>When this arrow strikes its target, conjuration magic creates grasping, poisonous brambles, which wrap around the target. The creature hit by the arrow takes an extra [[/damage 2d6 type=poison]] damage, its speed is reduced by 10 feet, and it takes [[/damage 2d6 type=slashing]] damage the first time on each turn it moves 1 foot or more without teleporting. The target or any creature that can reach it can use its action to remove the brambles with a successful Strength (&amp;Reference[skill=Athletics]) check against your Arcane Shot save DC. Otherwise, the brambles last for 1 minute or until you use this option again.</p><p>The poison damage and slashing damage both increase to [[/damage 4d6]] when you reach 18th level in this class.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div>",
